{
  "chapter": 18,
  "chapter_summary": "柳无眉向众人坦白，那个神秘人要求楚留香的人头作为解毒条件，否则她只剩两三个月寿命。李玉函以五名人质要挟楚留香自尽，并以暴雨梨花钉为赌注。楚留香利用心理战术，指出暴雨梨花钉可能是空的，趁李玉函分心之际一击夺下暗器。夫妻二人陷入绝望，众人为其深情所感动。胡铁花主动提出帮忙寻解药，但柳无眉拒绝透露神秘人身份，称其武功远超帅一帆、萧玉剑等人，即便联手也必死无疑。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我虽然不敢去见他，情势却逼得我非去见他不可。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "你到底见到了他没有?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "见着了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "他是不是能解你的毒呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "他自然能解，但他却有个条件。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "什么条件?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "他也没什么别的条件，只不过问我要一件东西。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "他要的是什么东西?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "他要的是楚留香的人头。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你脑袋里究竟有什么宝贝，为什么想要你脑袋的人竟有那么多?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我和你无冤无仇，本不忍为了这种事杀你的，但那人却说，我中毒已深，最多只有两三个月的寿命了，在这两三个月里，我若不能提着你的脑袋去见他，就只有赶快准备后事了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "现在已经过了多久?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "已有两个月。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "那人说的话靠得住么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你若知道他是谁，就绝不会怀疑他的话了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "我倒未想到你竟是如此怕死的人。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我并不是怕死，我只不过是……是……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "是什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "她只是为了我，她不忍抛下我一个人去死，现在你总该明白了吧?",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "明白了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你现在总该知道，她并不是石观音的奸细，更不是任何人的奸细，她想要你的命，只不过是想保全自己的性命而已。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "人不为己，天诛地灭，这点我绝不怪她，她这样做本是应该的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "既是如此，你就索性成全了她吧!",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "我方才已说过，人不为己，天诛地灭，所以我虽然很想帮她的忙，但至少也得先为自己打算打算。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "若要你砍下自己的脑袋去帮别人的忙，你肯不肯?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这个忙你不帮也不行。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "哦?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你若不肯死，我就要他们五个人的命，你总不忍眼见着他们五个人为你而死吧?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "你若杀死了他们，你们夫妻……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我们夫妻反正不想活了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "看来你的确是个痴情的人，为了自己的老婆，竟不惜做这种事……但你为什么不直接用这暴雨梨花钉来杀我呢?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我没有杀死你的把握，这已是我的最后一个赌注，我绝不能冒险。",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "至少你这句说的倒是老实话。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "现在话已说尽，你再拖下去也没有用了，我再给你片刻考虑，等到数到五字，你不死，他们就得死。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "数到五……?你为何不肯数到三呢?那样岂非更紧张刺激得多。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "一。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "二。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我现在才明白了两件事。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "什么事?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "我现在才知道'拥翠山庄'的子弟的确都不会做坏事的，因为你非但不懂得该如何去做坏事，甚至连该如何吓人都不懂。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "你若想叫别人怕你，你自己就千万不能害怕，你自己若先害怕起来，别人又怎么会怕你呢?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不错，这就正如懂得说笑话的人，自己绝对不会笑，他自己若先大笑起来，那么无论他说的笑话多有趣，别人也不会觉得好笑的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你们以为……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "像你们这样的世家子弟，还有个最大的毛病。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "你们最大的毛病就是江湖历练太少，因为你们根本用不着自己到江湖中去挣扎，去奋斗，你们的地位一生出来就注定要比别人高些，所以你们大都免不了有些目空一切，所以也就难免会粗心大意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "譬如说，这'暴雨梨花钉'现在正是你的救命护身符，你夫妻两人现在什么事全都要靠它了，但你事先有没有将它检查一遍，看看它的机簧是不是有了毛病?看看这匣子是不是空的?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "暴雨梨花钉从来万无一失……",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "世界上并没有一件事是永远不会出错的，连太阳都有被天狗星吞没的时候，这暴雨梨花钉又怎会绝对万无一失，也许它里面忽然生锈了呢?也许忽然有几个小虫钻进去，塞住了它的钉孔。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "何况，它就算真的是万无一失也没有用，因为它根本就是空的，昨天晚上我们对付'天罗地网'夫妻时，已将里面的梨花钉全射了出去。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你以为我是三岁的小孩子，就凭你这几句话就可以将我吓倒?老实告诉你，你说的话，我连一个字也不相信。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "你若不信，为何不自己瞧瞧?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我用不着瞧，根本用不着。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "女人，女人……女人真是妙得很。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "被她们这么样一哭，连我都忍不住以为该死的是楚留香我了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你……你准备将他们怎么样?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "他们已经有七次要杀我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但以后他们绝不会再害你了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我方才听他们说，他们只想找个没有人的地方，安安静静的过几个月，你……你就成全了他们吧!",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑珍珠",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不错，你放了他们吧!",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你的意思呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不能放……",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_tian_er",
      "speaker_name": "宋甜儿",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "为什么不能放?",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你这人为什么这样狠心呢?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "现在我们若让他们走，实在等于杀他们一样，因为柳无眉已活不长了，她一死，李玉函还能活下去么?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你……你难道想救他们?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "他们若杀了楚留香，固然是我的仇人，但现在他们并没有杀死楚留香，却救过我的命，所以他们不但是我的朋友，还是我的恩人。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我胡铁花难道还会眼看着救命恩人中毒而死么?",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_tian_er",
      "speaker_name": "宋甜儿",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你真是个好人。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_song_tian_er",
      "text": "你若再抱住我不放，我就要变成坏人了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "你只要说出能救你的那个人是谁，我们就可以帮你去向他要解药，他若不肯给，嘿嘿……我不打扁他的头才怪。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "你说吧，只要你说出来，他们一定有法子能将解药要回来的。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "无论多么困难的事，楚留香都有法子办得到的。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "你们实在太好了，你们对我的好意，我今生只怕再也无法报答。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "你说出来，就算报答了我们。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "我不能说。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "因为我若说出来，非但没有用，反而害了你们，我现在……现在实在不忍再害你们了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "你难道怕他们去为你要解药时被那人杀了么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "嗯!",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "你未免太看轻他们了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_tian_er",
      "speaker_name": "宋甜儿",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "到现在你难道还不相信他们有多大本事?",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_song_tian_er",
      "text": "若有人能从那人手上将解药夺来，我也不至于苦苦要杀楚留香了，你想，我既然能要帅一帆、萧玉剑、天罗地网这些人来害楚留香，自然也就能要他们去为我求解药，我为什么不这样做呢?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "凭那些武林前辈，难道都不能从那人手上将解药要回来?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "他们就算一起去，也要一起死在那人的手上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "你说那人竟能将帅一帆、萧玉剑、天罗地网这些人全都杀死?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "世上真有这样的人么，我实在有些不信。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    }
